{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Hi. I'm here to talk to you about the importance of"},{"time":4000,"text":"praise, admiration and thank you,"},{"time":7000,"text":"and having it be specific and genuine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":9000,"text":"And the way I got interested in this was,"},{"time":11000,"text":"I noticed in myself, when I was growing up,"},{"time":14000,"text":"and until about a few years ago,"},{"time":15000,"text":"that I would want to say thank you to someone,"},{"time":17000,"text":"I would want to praise them,"},{"time":18000,"text":"I would want to take in their praise of me"},{"time":20000,"text":"and I'd just stop it."},{"time":22000,"text":"And I asked myself, why?"},{"time":25000,"text":"I felt shy, I felt embarrassed."},{"time":27000,"text":"And then my question became,"},{"time":29000,"text":"am I the only one who does this?"},{"time":31000,"text":"So, I decided to investigate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":32000,"text":"I'm fortunate enough to work in the rehab facility,"},{"time":35000,"text":"so I get to see people who are facing life and death with addiction."},{"time":38000,"text":"And sometimes it comes down to something as simple as,"},{"time":42000,"text":"their core wound is their father died without ever saying he's proud of them."},{"time":47000,"text":"But then, they hear from all the family and friends"},{"time":49000,"text":"that the father told everybody else that he was proud of him,"},{"time":52000,"text":"but he never told the son."},{"time":53000,"text":"It's because he didn't know that his son needed to hear it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56000,"text":"So my question is, why don't we ask for the things that we need?"},{"time":60000,"text":"I know a gentleman, married for 25 years,"},{"time":62000,"text":"who's longing to hear his wife say,"},{"time":64000,"text":"\"Thank you for being the breadwinner, so I can stay home with the kids,\""},{"time":67000,"text":"but won't ask."},{"time":68000,"text":"I know a woman who's good at this."},{"time":70000,"text":"She, once a week, meets with her husband and says,"},{"time":72000,"text":"\"I'd really like you to thank me for all these things I did in the house and with the kids.\""},{"time":76000,"text":"And he goes, \"Oh, this is great, this is great.\""},{"time":79000,"text":"And praise really does have to be genuine,"},{"time":81000,"text":"but she takes responsibility for that."},{"time":83000,"text":"And a friend of mine, April, who I've had since kindergarten,"},{"time":86000,"text":"she thanks her children for doing their chores."},{"time":89000,"text":"And she said, \"Why wouldn't I thank it, even though they're supposed to do it?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":91000,"text":"So, the question is, why was I blocking it?"},{"time":93000,"text":"Why were other people blocking it?"},{"time":94000,"text":"Why can I say, \"I'll take my steak medium rare,"},{"time":97000,"text":"I need size six shoes,\" but I won't say,"},{"time":100000,"text":"\"Would you praise me this way?\""},{"time":102000,"text":"And it's because I'm giving you critical data about me."},{"time":106000,"text":"I'm telling you where I'm insecure."},{"time":108000,"text":"I'm telling you where I need your help."},{"time":110000,"text":"And I'm treating you, my inner circle,"},{"time":113000,"text":"like you're the enemy."},{"time":115000,"text":"Because what can you do with that data?"},{"time":117000,"text":"You could neglect me."},{"time":119000,"text":"You could abuse it."},{"time":120000,"text":"Or you could actually meet my need."}]},{"cues":[{"time":122000,"text":"And I took my bike into the bike store-- I love this --"},{"time":124000,"text":"same bike, and they'd do something called \"truing\" the wheels."},{"time":127000,"text":"The guy said, \"You know, when you true the wheels,"},{"time":129000,"text":"it's going to make the bike so much better.\""},{"time":130000,"text":"I get the same bike back,"},{"time":132000,"text":"and they've taken all the little warps out of those same wheels"},{"time":135000,"text":"I've had for two and a half years, and my bike is like new."},{"time":138000,"text":"So, I'm going to challenge all of you."},{"time":140000,"text":"I want you to true your wheels:"},{"time":142000,"text":"be honest about the praise that you need to hear."},{"time":145000,"text":"What do you need to hear? Go home to your wife --"},{"time":147000,"text":"go ask her, what does she need?"},{"time":149000,"text":"Go home to your husband -- what does he need?"},{"time":151000,"text":"Go home and ask those questions, and then help the people around you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":154000,"text":"And it's simple."},{"time":155000,"text":"And why should we care about this?"},{"time":157000,"text":"We talk about world peace."},{"time":158000,"text":"How can we have world peace with different cultures, different languages?"},{"time":161000,"text":"I think it starts household by household, under the same roof."},{"time":165000,"text":"So, let's make it right in our own backyard."},{"time":167000,"text":"And I want to thank all of you in the audience"},{"time":169000,"text":"for being great husbands, great mothers,"},{"time":171000,"text":"friends, daughters, sons."},{"time":173000,"text":"And maybe somebody's never said that to you,"},{"time":174000,"text":"but you've done a really, really good job."},{"time":176000,"text":"And thank you for being here, just showing up"},{"time":179000,"text":"and changing the world with your ideas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":182000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":184000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}